VI'm moving very quickly over a number of
p181
aVdisciplines. In biology, the notions of symbiosis,
p182
aVgroup selection, evolutionary psychology are contested, to be sure.
p183
aVBut there is really no longer any major debate over the fact that
p184
aVcooperative arrangements have moved from a peripheral role to a central role
p185
aVin biology, from the level of the cell to the level of the ecology.
p186
aVAnd again, our notions of individuals as economic beings
p187
aVhave been overturned.
p188
aVRational self-interest is not always the dominating factor.
p189
aVIn fact, people will act to punish cheaters, even at a cost to themselves.
